16
00:00:37,934 --> 00:00:40,267
There's a feature in HTML
that we really like.

17
00:00:40,267 --> 00:00:42,100
Remember, not XHTML.

18
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:46,334
HTML allows you
to leave out certain tags.

19
00:00:46,334 --> 00:00:48,467
Meiert: That means you don't
have to close

20
00:00:48,467 --> 00:00:49,968
