and other elements.

21
00:00:49,968 --> 00:00:53,634
You can entirely skip
your HTML head and body text,

22
00:00:53,634 --> 00:00:57,100
and that's something authors do
with tbody element anyways.

23
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:58,901
These texts
are entirely optional.

24
00:00:58,901 --> 00:01:01,334
And the HTML
will still be valid.

25
00:01:01,334 --> 00:01:03,534
Khaw: It takes a while
to get used to this technique.

26
00:01:03,534 --> 00:01:05,434
But leaving out optional texts

27
00:01:05,434 --> 00:01:07,033
will make your pages
a lot smaller

28
00:01:07,033 --> 00:01:09,234
and easier to understand.

29
00:01:09,234 --> 00:01:12,000
Meiert: Maybe one thing
we especially like about this

30
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,901
